Add Multiple Reference Lines to Charts

You can use any number of static or dynamic reference lines to mark up a chart. Dynamic reference lines are powered by existing queries in the dashboard.

Tap +Reference Line in the X-Axis or Y-Axis section of the chart widget panel.

Add either a static or dynamic value for the reference line.

Select a default or custom color.
